                <li>‚úì Be direct, caring, and calm</li>
                <li>‚úì Don't debate whether suicide is right or wrong</li>
                <li>‚úì Avoid trying to guilt them out of it</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Keep Them Safe</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">
                If they're in immediate danger, don't leave them alone. Remove any means of self-harm if possible. Call 911 or take them to the nearest emergency room.
